reviewText: I was a big Mikkola fan back the 1970s when I was racing and was excited about getting this.  This DVD is more of a Yamaha promotional video than anything.  It is quite dry and goes on and on about how good Yamaha motocross bikes are.  this is a marketing video, not a legitimate documentary.
A need to see if you like vintage mx,me and all my moto buddies enjoyed it,will be watch again and again
